WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.150 align:middle line:90%


00:00:11.150 --> 00:00:12.810 align:middle line:90%
>>Life is a journey.

00:00:12.810 --> 00:00:14.330 align:middle line:90%
We are born.

00:00:14.330 --> 00:00:16.370 align:middle line:90%
Our lives are lived.

00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:18.240 align:middle line:90%
Then we die.

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:19.740 align:middle line:90%
No one can live forever.

00:00:19.740 --> 00:00:21.910 align:middle line:90%
Or can they?

00:00:21.910 --> 00:00:24.280 align:middle line:84%
The goal of this film
is to try to understand

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:29.050 align:middle line:84%
the basic fundamental questions,
what happens when we die?

00:00:29.050 --> 00:00:31.550 align:middle line:90%
What is the purpose of life?

00:00:31.550 --> 00:00:33.340 align:middle line:84%
As we set out to
find the answers,

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:37.880 align:middle line:84%
we began to see that we were
on a journey, an adventure.

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:41.280 align:middle line:84%
Like any journey, we
discovered we were on a path.

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:43.360 align:middle line:84%
To help answer
these questions, we

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:46.685 align:middle line:84%
set out to talk to 12 experts
in the field of energy

00:00:46.685 --> 00:00:47.435 align:middle line:90%
and consciousness.

00:00:47.435 --> 00:00:50.770 align:middle line:90%


00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.220 align:middle line:84%
>>Do I, this thing I
