experiences with contact

00:10:54.110 --> 00:10:57.120 align:middle line:84%
of people on the other
side through fax machines,

00:10:57.120 --> 00:11:02.760 align:middle line:84%
through computers, through all
kinds of technological devices.

00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:05.390 align:middle line:84%
And so that kind of opened
something up for me.

00:11:05.390 --> 00:11:08.090 align:middle line:84%
I went, that was
not my imagination.

00:11:08.090 --> 00:11:09.570 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what it was.

00:11:09.570 --> 00:11:12.770 align:middle line:84%
But I'm just going to hold that
as a little piece to go forward

00:11:12.770 --> 00:11:15.270 align:middle line:90%
with.

00:11:15.270 --> 00:11:18.290 align:middle line:84%
>>I had, for instance,
an experience

00:11:18.290 --> 00:11:26.290 align:middle line:84%
of finding myself, moving
along in this other dimension.

00:11:26.290 --> 00:11:28.040 align:middle line:90%
And I say moving.

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.617 align:middle line:84%
Was I in my body
or out of my body?

00:11:29.617 --> 00:11:30.450 align:middle line:90%
I don't really know.

00:11:30.450 --> 00:11:33.756 align:middle line:84%
And it wasn't significant
to me at the time.

00:11:33.756 --> 00:11:38.290 align:middle line:90%
But I found myself moving along.

00:11:38.290 --> 00:11:40.610 align:middle line:84%
And off to my left,
all of a sudden,

00:11:40.610 --> 00:11:42.030 align:middle line:84%
there were these
beings of light.

00:11:42.030 --> 00:11:44.520 align:middle line:84%
And they were gathered
around in a circle.

00:11:44.520 --> 00:11:46.750 align:middle line:90%
And I almost went right by them.

00:11:46.750 --> 00:11:51.100 align:middle line:84%
I was kind of, oh,
well, that's something.

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:52.924 align:middle line:90%
You don't see that every day.

00:11:52.924 --> 00:11:54.632 align:middle line:84%
So I thought I'd go
over and investigate.

00:11:54.632 --> 00:11:56.740 align:middle line:84%
And so I peeked
over the shoulder

00:11:56.740 --> 00:11:58.320 align:middle line:90%
of one of these light people.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:11:59.110 align:middle line:90%
And I looked down.

00:11:59.110 --> 00:12:01.720 align:middle line:84%
And there was some guy down
there that had obviously

00:12:01.720 --> 00:12:05.120 align:middle line:84%
just crossed over
from being dead,

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:07.390 align:middle line:84%
from going through
the process, and now

00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:09.690 align:middle line:84%
was on the other
side of something.

00:12:09.690 --> 00:12:11.060 align:middle line:90%
I didn't even know where I was.

00:12:11.060 --> 00:12:13.640 align:middle line:90%


00:12:13.640 --> 00:12:16.910 align:middle line:84%
The closer I looked
though, the more

00:12:16.910 --> 00:12:20.770 align:middle line:84%
I realized that that person that
was down there was my father.

00:12:20.770 --> 00:12:23.680 align:middle line:90%


00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:25.790 align:middle line:84%
Now, my father had
died about seven years

00:12:25.790 --> 00:12:28.120 align:middle line:84%
before that of
Alzheimer's disease.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:34.270 align:middle line:84%
And he had gone through a
process of gradual degradation.

00:12:34.270 --> 00:12:35.560 align:middle line:90%
He was a brilliant guy.

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:38.150 align:middle line:84%
And it was really
tough to watch him

00:12:38.150 --> 00:12:43.580 align:middle line:84%
lose so much of his essence, to
the point where he didn't even

00:12:43.580 --> 00:12:47.440 align:middle line:84%
recognize us anymore
for the most part.

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:50.990 align:middle line:84%
I was with him the
night that he died.

00:12:50.990 --> 00:12:57.980 align:middle line:84%
And I whispered to him the
night that he was clearly

00:12:57.980 --> 00:12:58.750 align:middle line:90%
passing away.

00:12:58.750 --> 00:13:01.710 align:middle line:84%
I said to him, Dad, when
you get to the other side,

00:13:01.710 --> 00:13:05.400 align:middle line:84%
will you come back and
tell me what it's like?

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:07.560 align:middle line:84%
And it was just one
of those moments

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:09.477 align:middle line:90%
of a little bit of clarity.

00:13:09.477 --> 00:13:10.310 align:middle line:90%
And he looked at me.

00:13:10.310 --> 00:13:13.820 align:middle line:90%
And he nodded.

00:13:13.820 --> 00:13:18.180 align:middle line:84%
And so I never would have
dreamed that I might actually

00:13:18.180 --> 00:13:25.120 align:middle line:84%
be in a position to be welcoming
him over to the other side.

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:25.946 align:middle line:90%
But yet here I was.

00:13:25.946 --> 00:13:26.820 align:middle line:90%
I was looking at him.

00:13:26.820 --> 00:13:30.140 align:middle line:84%
And I instinctively
picked him up in my arms.

00:13:30.140 --> 00:13:31.330 align:middle line:90%
And I started carrying him.

00:13:31.330 --> 00:13:35.970 align:middle line:84%
And I was telling him that,
Dad, now you've passed over

00:13:35.970 --> 00:13:38.620 align:middle line:84%
and that your family's
going to come and get you.

00:13:38.620 --> 00:13:40.090 align:middle line:90%
And it just seem so natural.

00:13:40.090 --> 00:13:43.450 align:middle line:84%
And again, I never would
have dreamed that any of this

00:13:43.450 --> 00:13:44.430 align:middle line:90%
would be possible.

00:13:44.430 --> 00:13:47.800 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't have made
it up if I'd tried.

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:50.000 align:middle line:84%
And after awhile, the
beings of light came.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.690 align:middle line:90%
And they took him away from me.

00:13:51.690 --> 00:13:54.230 align:middle line:84%
And they said that
his family is coming.

00:13:54.230 --> 00:13:58.520 align:middle line:90%
And he's going to be all right.

00:13:58.520 --> 00:14:01.130 align:middle line:90%
And we can care for him now.

00:14:01.130 --> 00:14:02.880 align:middle line:84%
And I came out of
that experience

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:11.280 align:middle line:84%
so-- there aren't words to
talk about something like that.

00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:16.620 align:middle line:84%
Because you try to tell
somebody about death.

00:14:16.620 --> 00:14:18.000 align:middle line:90%
And they weren't there.

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.750 align:middle line:90%
And it's just words.

00:14:19.750 --> 00:14:24.230 align:middle line:84%
But to me it was so
profound in so many ways.

00:14:24.230 --> 00:14:26.790 align:middle line:84%
Because it wrapped
up so much emotion

00:14:26.790 --> 00:14:29.570 align:middle line:84%
that I had around his
Alzheimer's and seeing

00:14:29.570 --> 00:14:31.350 align:middle line:90%
him pass.

00:14:31.350 --> 00:14:35.310 align:middle line:84%
It opened up the possibility
that maybe the range

00:14:35.310 --> 00:14:36.890 align:middle line:84%
of experience in
the physical world

00:14:36.890 --> 00:14:42.450 align:middle line:84%
is not so separate
from the world beyond

00:14:42.450 --> 00:14:44.750 align:middle line:84%
and that maybe we
have capacities

00:14:44.750 --> 00:14:48.160 align:middle line:84%
of moving between those
two worlds in ways

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:51.100 align:middle line:84%
that, unfortunately, we
maybe knew at one time.

00:14:51.100 --> 00:14:53.840 align:middle line:84%
But we've lost the
capacity to do that.

00:14:53.840 --> 00:14:57.970 align:middle line:84%
>>My wife has had actually
many profound out-of-body

00:14:57.970 --> 00:14:59.810 align:middle line:90%
experiences.

00:14:59.810 --> 00:15:02.855 align:middle line:84%
The day her father died,
she was on the couch.

00:15:02.855 --> 00:15:04.500 align:middle line:90%
She was exhausted.

00:15:04.500 --> 00:15:06.110 align:middle line:84%
Her mother called
her and told her.

00:15:06.110 --> 00:15:07.910 align:middle line:90%
We're in another state.

00:15:07.910 --> 00:15:13.620 align:middle line:84%
And to make a long story
short, this is about 2 o'clock

00:15:13.620 --> 00:15:14.560 align:middle line:90%
in the morning.

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:16.320 align:middle line:90%
And she lays down.

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:18.030 align:middle line:84%
We had just made a
flight to go back

00:15:18.030 --> 00:15:21.730 align:middle line:84%
to Baltimore to
attend the funeral.

00:15:21.730 --> 00:15:22.596 align:middle line:90%
She lays down.

00:15:22.596 --> 00:15:23.970 align:middle line:84%
The next thing
she knows, she has

00:15:23.970 --> 00:15:26.390 align:middle line:84%
this spontaneous
out-of-body experience.

00:15:26.390 --> 00:15:30.420 align:middle line:84%
And she finds herself in her
basement of her mother's house.

00:15:30.420 --> 00:15:37.590 align:middle line:84%
And there is her father there
with, of all people, my mother.

00:15:37.590 --> 00:15:41.390 align:middle line:84%
And her father, who was
very sickly, couldn't walk,

00:15:41.390 --> 00:15:42.480 align:middle line:90%
was in very bad shape.

00:15:42.480 --> 00:15:44.670 align:middle line:90%
He was dying of cancer.

00:15:44.670 --> 00:15:47.150 align:middle line:84%
He literally jumped up
and clicked his heels,

00:15:47.150 --> 00:15:53.240 align:middle line:84%
she said, and was showing her
how vibrant and alive he was.

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:56.890 align:middle line:84%
He was proving to her that,
look, don't grieve for me.

00:15:56.890 --> 00:15:59.020 align:middle line:90%
I'm feeling great.

00:15:59.020 --> 00:16:01.800 align:middle line:84%
And, of course,
out-of-body, people

00:16:01.800 --> 00:16:03.420 align:middle line:90%
communicate not by words.

00:16:03.420 --> 00:16:06.120 align:middle line:84%
They communicate by
thought transference.

00:16:06.120 --> 00:16:08.880 align:middle line:90%
It's just normal communication.

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:12.510 align:middle line:84%
And, of course, he communicated
his love for his daughter.

00:16:12.510 --> 00:16:15.500 align:middle line:84%
But most importantly, he
was making it very clear

00:16:15.500 --> 00:16:18.300 align:middle line:90%
that he was doing great.

00:16:18.300 --> 00:16:21.190 align:middle line:84%
And he was glad to
be where he was.

00:16:21.190 --> 00:16:25.250 align:middle line:84%
And my mother and
my wife's father

00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:27.850 align:middle line:90%
were basically having a party.

00:16:27.850 --> 00:16:29.520 align:middle line:84%
For lack of a better
word, they were

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:34.450 align:middle line:84%
having a party, a
very joyous party.

00:16:34.450 --> 00:16:39.940 align:middle line:84%
And so my wife, after
that, she immediately

00:16:39.940 --> 00:16:42.740 align:middle line:84%
come back and was
like, oh my God.

00:16:42.740 --> 00:16:45.730 align:middle line:84%
But all the fear-based
ideas just were gone.

00:16:45.730 --> 00:16:46.980 align:middle line:90%
She was just ecstatic.

00:16:46.980 --> 00:16:50.630 align:middle line:84%
It was a confirmation to her
that everything is just not

00:16:50.630 --> 00:16:54.560 align:middle line:90%
only good, it's great.

00:16:54.560 --> 00:16:58.653 align:middle line:84%
Her concept of death was just
so negative, so restrictive.

00:16:58.653 --> 00:17:01.470 align:middle line:90%


00:17:01.470 --> 00:17:05.380 align:middle line:84%
There's very few positives in
our culture attached to death.

00:17:05.380 --> 00:17:07.890 align:middle line:84%
And here she learned, I
think, a valuable lesson

00:17:07.890 --> 00:17:10.230 align:middle line:90%
that it's not a negative event.

00:17:10.230 --> 00:17:12.450 align:middle line:90%
It's a very positive event.

00:17:12.450 --> 00:17:14.040 align:middle line:90%
It's an uplifting event.

00:17:14.040 --> 00:17:18.700 align:middle line:84%
He was free from the pain
of this physical body.

00:17:18.700 --> 00:17:22.020 align:middle line:84%
And he was finally
free to enjoy himself.

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:28.037 align:middle line:84%
So to me, I thought it was
quite a remarkable experience.

00:17:28.037 --> 00:17:29.870 align:middle line:84%
And I think it must
have been a great lesson

00:17:29.870 --> 00:17:32.030 align:middle line:90%
that she needed on some level.

00:17:32.030 --> 00:17:35.000 align:middle line:90%
>>My uncle had cancer.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:38.609 align:middle line:90%
And I offered to send him Reiki.

00:17:38.609 --> 00:17:39.650 align:middle line:90%
He lived in Poughkeepsie.

00:17:39.650 --> 00:17:42.030 align:middle line:90%
And I lived in Saratoga.

00:17:42.030 --> 00:17:44.630 align:middle line:84%
I offered to send
him Reiki every day.

00:17:44.630 --> 00:17:47.000 align:middle line:84%
And we agreed on 8
o'clock in the morning.

00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:56.940 align:middle line:90%


00:17:56.940 --> 00:18:00.030 align:middle line:84%
8 o'clock in the morning, he
sat down in his living room.

00:18:00.030 --> 00:18:01.670 align:middle line:90%
I sat down in my Reiki room.

00:18:01.670 --> 00:18:03.290 align:middle line:90%
And I sent him Reiki.

00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:04.270 align:middle line:90%
He was an engineer.

00:18:04.270 --> 00:18:06.390 align:middle line:84%
The stuff didn't particularly
make sense to him.

00:18:06.390 --> 00:18:06.980 align:middle line:90%
It was fine.

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:07.880 align:middle line:90%
He liked it.

00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:11.160 align:middle line:84%
But he wasn't really
sure much was happening.

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:14.530 align:middle line:84%
But he was willing to sit and
let me send him Reiki every day

00:18:14.530 --> 00:18:15.400 align:middle line:90%
at 8 o'clock.

00:18:15.400 --> 00:18:18.770 align:middle line:84%
So we met at 8
o'clock in the ethers.

00:18:18.770 --> 00:18:22.320 align:middle line:90%
And I sent him Reiki.

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:24.280 align:middle line:90%
This started in August.

00:18:24.280 --> 00:18:27.780 align:middle line:84%
In November, I sat down
to send them Reiki.

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:32.790 align:middle line:84%
For three days in a
row, I felt so ecstatic.

00:18:32.790 --> 00:18:34.890 align:middle line:90%
I was feeling such euphoria.

00:18:34.890 --> 00:18:38.440 align:middle line:90%
I was convinced he was healing.

00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:40.954 align:middle line:84%
A few days later,
one of my cousins

00:18:40.954 --> 00:18:43.120 align:middle line:84%
called to say that they had
just been to the doctor.

00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:46.870 align:middle line:90%
And dad had six months to live.

00:18:46.870 --> 00:18:48.540 align:middle line:90%
I was confounded.

00:18:48.540 --> 00:18:52.910 align:middle line:84%
But I was so sure some
healing had happened.

00:18:52.910 --> 00:18:55.340 align:middle line:90%
And then I remembered.

00:18:55.340 --> 00:18:57.160 align:middle line:90%
Healing isn't always physical.

00:18:57.160 --> 00:19:00.040 align:middle line:84%
So I thought something
healed for him.

00:19:00.040 --> 00:19:00.790 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what.

00:19:00.790 --> 00:19:03.480 align:middle line:90%


00:19:03.480 --> 00:19:05.550 align:middle line:84%
Then in January, he
was in the hospital.

00:19:05.550 --> 00:19:06.520 align:middle line:90%
He was very ill.

00:19:06.520 --> 00:19:07.700 align:middle line:90%
And I went to Poughkeepsie.

00:19:07.700 --> 00:19:11.940 align:middle line:84%
And I was giving him Reiki in
the ICU, quite late at night.

00:19:11.940 --> 00:19:12.940 align:middle line:90%
And he was dosing.

00:19:12.940 --> 00:19:13.950 align:middle line:90%
And then he'd wake.

00:19:13.950 --> 00:19:16.320 align:middle line:90%
And we'd chat a little bit.

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:17.860 align:middle line:84%
And I felt comfortable
to tell him

00:19:17.860 --> 00:19:20.620 align:middle line:84%
what I had experienced
in November.

00:19:20.620 --> 00:19:22.100 align:middle line:84%
During this time
when I was feeling

00:19:22.100 --> 00:19:25.940 align:middle line:84%
this ecstasy and this euphoria,
I heard his wife's laughter.

00:19:25.940 --> 00:19:28.200 align:middle line:90%
She had died three years before.

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:30.130 align:middle line:90%
He adored his wife.

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:32.500 align:middle line:90%
And I was hearing her laughter.

00:19:32.500 --> 00:19:35.300 align:middle line:90%
And it was so exciting.

00:19:35.300 --> 00:19:36.890 align:middle line:90%
And I told him about this.

00:19:36.890 --> 00:19:39.890 align:middle line:90%
And he said, yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:19:39.890 --> 00:19:44.000 align:middle line:84%
I knew I was soaking
up something wonderful.

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:45.990 align:middle line:84%
So even though he
said that he didn't

00:19:45.990 --> 00:19:49.020 align:middle line:84%
feel Reiki when I sent it
to him from a distance,

00:19:49.020 --> 00:19:53.620 align:middle line:84%
at that time something
changed for him.

00:19:53.620 --> 00:19:55.970 align:middle line:90%
And he died.

00:19:55.970 --> 00:19:59.230 align:middle line:90%
Healing doesn't mean curing.

00:19:59.230 --> 00:20:01.610 align:middle line:90%
Healing can be spiritual.

00:20:01.610 --> 00:20:02.720 align:middle line:90%
It can be emotional.

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:04.310 align:middle line:90%
It can be psychological.

00:20:04.310 --> 00:20:07.275 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what
healed for him.

00:20:07.275 --> 00:20:09.090 align:middle line:90%
But something did.

00:20:09.090 --> 00:20:12.140 align:middle line:84%
And the gift he gave
me was telling me

00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:14.510 align:middle line:84%
he knew something
good had happened.

00:20:14.510 --> 00:20:17.800 align:middle line:90%


00:20:17.800 --> 00:20:21.160 align:middle line:84%
His daughter and I liked to
talk about our understanding

00:20:21.160 --> 00:20:23.400 align:middle line:90%
of metaphysics.

00:20:23.400 --> 00:20:26.180 align:middle line:84%
So we would tell him things
that we'd been reading

00:20:26.180 --> 00:20:30.520 align:middle line:84%
and what we thought might
happen for him when he passed.

00:20:30.520 --> 00:20:33.220 align:middle line:90%
And he listened.

00:20:33.220 --> 00:20:34.822 align:middle line:90%
He always was open to listening.

00:20:34.822 --> 00:20:36.530 align:middle line:84%
It didn't make sense
to him particularly.

00:20:36.530 --> 00:20:38.571 align:middle line:84%
He didn't even tell us
that it didn't make sense.

00:20:38.571 --> 00:20:41.560 align:middle line:90%


00:20:41.560 --> 00:20:44.580 align:middle line:84%
Three days after
he died, I sat down

00:20:44.580 --> 00:20:47.760 align:middle line:90%
to meditate in my Reiki room.

00:20:47.760 --> 00:20:50.030 align:middle line:90%
And I closed my eyes.

00:20:50.030 --> 00:20:54.110 align:middle line:84%
And it was as if he was
right there in front of me.

00:20:54.110 --> 00:20:56.500 align:middle line:90%
It was very real.

00:20:56.500 --> 00:21:00.950 align:middle line:84%
He said, I want to tell you,
everything you and Betsy said,

00:21:00.950 --> 00:21:01.930 align:middle line:90%
I didn't understand.

00:21:01.930 --> 00:21:03.950 align:middle line:90%
It didn't make any sense to me.

00:21:03.950 --> 00:21:06.430 align:middle line:90%
But you were right.

00:21:06.430 --> 00:21:10.400 align:middle line:84%
And I saw him with
his beloved wife.

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:12.810 align:middle line:84%
They were all dressed up like
they were going to a party.

00:21:12.810 --> 00:21:14.560 align:middle line:84%
And they were in the
prime of their life.

00:21:14.560 --> 00:21:15.842 align:middle line:90%
They looked beautiful.

00:21:15.842 --> 00:21:17.800 align:middle line:84%
They had their arms around
each other's waists.

00:21:17.800 --> 00:21:19.216 align:middle line:84%
And they were
spinning in a circle

00:21:19.216 --> 00:21:20.640 align:middle line:90%
with their heads thrown back.

00:21:20.640 --> 00:21:25.180 align:middle line:84%
And it was a picture
of utter bliss.

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:28.340 align:middle line:90%
What a gift he gave me.

00:21:28.340 --> 00:21:31.660 align:middle line:90%
It was very sweet.

