I fell off the roof

01:00:16.530 --> 01:00:19.970 align:middle line:84%
opened up in space
all over again,

01:00:19.970 --> 01:00:22.340 align:middle line:90%
which was both gift and curse.

01:00:22.340 --> 01:00:25.270 align:middle line:84%
Because on the one hand, it
was a rediscovery of something

01:00:25.270 --> 01:00:29.350 align:middle line:84%
