wonderful and powerful for me.

01:00:29.350 --> 01:00:32.470 align:middle line:84%
On the other hand, it
only increased the tension

01:00:32.470 --> 01:00:35.070 align:middle line:90%
with my role as a pastor.

01:00:35.070 --> 01:00:40.040 align:middle line:84%
