out of the door of the church,

01:00:42.710 --> 01:00:45.080 align:middle line:84%
I got a call from
the Institute here

01:00:45.080 --> 01:00:48.230 align:middle line:84%
asking me if I would like to
become a residential trainer.

01:00:48.230 --> 01:00:53.160 align:middle line:84%
But the real force
