altered perceptions,

01:00:59.610 --> 01:01:01.760 align:middle line:90%
the metaphysical world.

01:01:01.760 --> 01:01:05.150 align:middle line:84%
And again, for me, the
most compelling component

01:01:05.150 --> 01:01:07.600 align:middle line:84%
